stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending_registration : mint (controller generates 32 bytes,<br/>delivers via SSH)
    pending_registration --> registered : agent presents on WebSocket handshake,<br/>controller verifies hash
    registered --> registered : agent reconnects<br/>(same token)
    registered --> rotating : periodic (24h)<br/>or admin command
    rotating --> registered : challenge/response<br/>new token issued
    registered --> revoked : admin revokes
    rotating --> revoked : admin revokes
    revoked --> [*] : WebSocket closed<br/>(code RevokedAuthToken)<br/>supervisor does not restart
